reviewText: I was 11yrs old when i heard this lady sing and it changed my life in music. If you like Mariachi music you will love this one. I already had this one but it wore out and it was a VHS. I am going to order it again.

I can,t say to much about this lady,I have been a fan of this lady and her singjng since I was little.her movies gets your attention, when you see them. I wish there were more dvds about this great lady.
